<section class='retreat-description'>
  <div class="retreat-banner">
    <h6>To hear the Word of God is a good thing, but it is not enough; so James says, “Do not merely listen to the word”. Rather than just hearing the Word, we are to “Do what it says”. Now, what does the Word says that we are to do?</h6>
  </div>
  <div class="retreat-desc">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="large-12 columns">
        <div class="retreat-desc-heading">
          <h2>About The Retreat</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="large-6 columns retreat-desc-body"><b>What's the theme about?</b><br><p>This years retreat is based off of James 1:22 "Do not merely hear the word and so deceive yourselves. Do what it says.". The idea behind the theme is that simply hearing the Word of God is not enough. The Word of God is living and it compels us to live out our faith, not be complacent about it. We are tempted when we are in trouble to believe that just hearing the truth, or "knowing" the truth is enough. James tells his readers that when they hear, but do not integrate what they hear into their lives that they are deceiving themselves.</p></div>
        <div class="large-6 columns retreat-desc-body"><p><b>What do we hope you get out of this retreat?</b><br>Youth members say that "they want the youth fellowship to grow, to be more united". That can't happen unless the members of the youth fellowship are active, not just in social events but in also learning the Word. Each of us were given the ability to act on our faith with the talents that God has given us. We are to use them to bring glory to Him. Simply sitting by in your faith is to be like the servant who hid the talent that the master had given him. Instead of growing his talent, he hid it and was later stripped of his talent and sent away from the master. If you want things to happen, <u>DO</u> something about it.</div>
        <div class="large-12 columns retreat-desc-body">
          <p>
            <b>What're some topics that will be covered?</b>
            <ul>
              <li>Significance of the Word</li>
              <li>The Working and Effects of God's Word</li>
              <li>How Do We Respond to God's Word</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="large-12 columns">
        <div class="retreat-desc-heading">
          <h3>Promotional Video</h3>
        </div>
        <video class="promo_video" controls src="http://files.tmcyf.org/vid/promo.mp4"></video>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
